   "source": [
    "## Troubleshooting\n",
    "\n",
    "**If you encounter issues:**\n",
    "\n",
    "1. **\"Module not found\" errors**: Make sure all files are in `/content/scraper/src/` with proper `__init__.py` files\n",
    "2. **Browser crashes**: Colab has limited resources. Try reducing `max_scroll_attempts` in config\n",
    "3. **No results found**: Google Maps may be blocking requests. Try a different location or wait before retrying\n",
    "4. **CAPTCHA triggered**: The scraper will fail if Google blocks the request. Try a smaller area or fewer scrolls\n",
    "\n",
    "**To check logs:**"
   ]
